CHANGES MADE (as required by the "indicate if changes were made" term of CC BY)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  This is a digital, single-device "pass-and-play" adaptation. It implements the
  official ruleset and additionally provides:
    • A configurable rules engine (player counts, deck, board powers, thresholds,
      voting modes) with validation.
    • The Communist / "Secret Hitler XL" third-faction variant (opt-in).
    • AI bots to fill seats.
    • Original user-interface, original artwork (e.g. the app icon), and original
      synthesized sound. NO official Secret Hitler artwork is included.

